    "body": "This is more precisely described as:\n\n\"Feature Request: %run searches PYTHONPATH (or sys.path)\"\n\nThis can easily be implemented by using a custom file-search function in:\n\n```\nip = get_ipython()\nip.magic_run('myscript.py' file_finder=my_finder_func)\n```\n"
  },
